---
// ArchiveLore.astro - Системные логи истории проекта
---

<section class="system-section lore-logs">
	<div class="section-header">
		<span class="cmd-prefix">></span> cat root/var/log/marketlab_history.log
	</div>

	<div class="log-entries">
		<div class="log-entry">
			<span class="log-timestamp">[2024.11.05 09:00:00]</span>
			<span class="log-tag">[SYSTEM]</span>
			<span class="log-msg">Инициализация ядра MARKETLAB. Сектор Emily активирован.</span>
		</div>
		<div class="log-entry">
			<span class="log-timestamp">[2024.12.10 14:35:22]</span>
			<span class="log-tag">[NETWORK]</span>
			<span class="log-msg">Установлено соединение с ByBit API. Проверка волатильности пройдена.</span>
		</div>
		<div class="log-entry warning">
			<span class="log-timestamp">[2025.01.15 22:10:05]</span>
			<span class="log-tag">[ALERT]</span>
			<span class="log-msg">Обнаружена аномалия в BTC/USDT. Переход в режим повышенной готовности.</span>
		</div>
		<div class="log-entry info">
			<span class="log-timestamp">[2025.12.21 12:00:00]</span>
			<span class="log-tag">[CORE]</span>
			<span class="log-msg">Запуск реактора Flux Capacitor. Энергоснабжение системы стабильно.</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.system-section {
		margin-bottom: 40px;
		border: 1px solid var(--term-dim);
		padding: 15px;
		background: var(--term-bg);
	}

	.section-header {
		color: var(--term-amber);
		margin-bottom: 15px;
	}

	.log-entries {
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 5px;
	}

	.log-entry {
		display: flex;
		gap: 10px;
		opacity: 0.8;
	}

	.log-timestamp { color: var(--term-dim); }
	.log-tag { color: var(--term-blue); font-weight: bold; }
	.log-msg { color: var(--term-green); opacity: 0.9; }

	.warning { opacity: 1; border-left: 2px solid var(--term-amber); padding-left: 10px; }
	.warning .log-tag { color: var(--term-amber); }

	.info { opacity: 1; border-left: 2px solid var(--term-green); padding-left: 10px; }
	
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.log-entry { flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
	}
</style>

